<P>MANY feel a &s;uperfluous unea&s;ine&s;s for want
of due attention to the following truth.</P>
<P>WE are oftentimes in &s;u&s;pen&s;e betwixt the
choice of different pur&s;uits. We chu&s;e one at
la&s;t doubtingly, and with an unconquered han|kering
